}
```

### Example 2: JavaScript SDK (Direct Format)

**URL**: https://a2aprotocol.ai/docs/guide/a2a-javascript-sdk

**Response Format Shown**:
```json
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "1",
  "result": {  // ← No "task" wrapper
    "id": "task-123",
    "kind": "task",
    "contextId": "ctx-456",
