### What happened?

`SecurityScheme` is defined in the spec as:

https://github.com/a2aproject/A2A/blob/e8c0f0fd610351987dee368aded7195154699e2b/specification/grpc/a2a.proto#L559-L577

Note of these definitions provides a `type` field but the doc provides an example with one at https://github.com/a2aproject/A2A/blob/main/docs/specification.md#85-sample-agent-card

```
